==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: anesthetize
<hw>anesthetize</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cause to become
unconscious by administration of an anaesthetic agent.</def>
<altsp>[Also spelled <asp>anaesthetize</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> put to sleep, put under, put out.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>anesthetized</ent>⟦br⟧
